{"Sid":0,"Did":118267,"Id":"282786","Title":"淡蘭便道","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-23/d5762221-76ee-4739-b042-ac0232cc08bc/collection/5bbe689a-9099-4e9a-9840-31c19b30d73a/108-sea-pa-222-201911082147035dc546ef2fc1a0.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n清代自淡蘭官道僻建以後，行旅稱便，入蘭移民日漸增多，於是另一條由台北木柵到石碇，經坪林入蘭的便道也開始出現移民的步伐，這一條由台北經坪林、烏桶、三分子、碧湖、石牌通猴洞坑隘口的道路，就是現今北宜公路的前身。 日人據台後，基於軍事需要，由宮尾泰利於1898（明治31）年10月，召集民工，重新修建，費時七月完成，全程共計65公里。二次世界大戰爆發後，日本又因國防軍事考量，再次拓寬北宜公路，及至日本戰敗，國民政府接收後，於1946年成立公路局，才正式開始交通客運營運。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.7930247","Keyword_Latitude":"24.8507676","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/EEBF8B53-B8A6-4854-B92D-25D278145479","Original_Identifier":"282786","Keyword_Subject_1":"空間、地域與遷徙","alias":"","Keywords":"北宜公路 / 宮尾泰利 / 淡蘭便道","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/23 23:54:00","timelines":"","place":"","address":"宜蘭縣頭城鎮北宜公路","longitude":"121.7930247","latitude":"24.8507676","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"","writer":"莊文生;鄭文嵐","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-23/d5762221-76ee-4739-b042-ac0232cc08bc/collectionOpen/35beeb9a-fad9-4060-b850-79bca6e481e8/108-sea-pa-222-re-201911082149145dc546ef2fc1a0.jpg"}}